    "body": "We only support the format-related arguments because Hardhat's `console.log` has it, beyond that I think using Solidity and the `vm.toString` cheatcodes are enough - changing e.g. `writeLine` to your example is a lot more complex since we'd essentially have to revisit all cheatcodes that accept strings and add a new signature that supports formats with a long list of arguments. Closing this as out of scope for that reason, but we can revisit if it turns out there is a lot of demand for it :)",
